info.name: mutuallyExclusiveFieldsWithoutAggregation_FU
info.description: Change the `fields` parameter of the getFinancials request to request mutually exclusive financial fields that cannot logically be combined, e.g., fields=['INCOME', 'EXPENSE', 'NET_INCOME'] without aggregation, to test invalid field combination violating business logic.
